<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>KasirPro Mobile Dashboard</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Versi mobile dashboard admin KasirPro untuk pengelolaan produk, penjualan, laporan, dan pengaturan." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#f7f3ea;
      --bg-soft:#efe7d7;
      --panel:#fffaf0cc;
      --panel-solid:#fffaf0;
      --text:#1d1a16;
      --muted:#6f6558;
      --line:#d8ccb8;
      --brand:#1f6f57;
      --brand-2:#d9923b;
      --brand-3:#8d3b2e;
      --accent:#f2c46d;
      --shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(56, 37, 14, .12);
      --radius:24px;
      --radius-sm:16px;
      --radius-xs:12px;
      --max:520px;
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{
      margin:0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(217,146,59,.18), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at left 20%, rgba(31,111,87,.13), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f9f5ed 0%, #f4ecdd 100%);
      color:var(--text);
      font-family:"Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
      min-height:100vh;
    }

    body.menu-open{
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .app{
      max-width:var(--max);
      margin:0 auto;
      min-height:100vh;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
      border-left:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.04);
      border-right:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.04);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,250,240,.72), rgba(255,250,240,.48));
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .texture,
    .texture::before,
    .texture::after{
      position:absolute;
      inset:auto;
      pointer-events:none;
      content:"";
    }

    .texture::before{
      width:180px;
      height:180px;
      top:-40px;
      right:-50px;
      border-radius:36px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(31,111,87,.16), rgba(217,146,59,.08));
      transform:rotate(18deg);
      filter:blur(2px);
    }

    .texture::after{
      width:140px;
      height:140px;
      left:-40px;
      top:320px;
      border:1px solid rgba(141,59,46,.15);
      border-radius:50%;
    }

    .mobile-nav{
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      z-index:30;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      padding:14px 16px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background:rgba(249,245,237,.82);
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(111,101,88,.12);
    }

    .brand{
      display:flex;
      gap:12px;
      align-items:center;
      min-width:0;
    }

    .brand-mark{
      width:44px;
      height:44px;
      border-radius:14px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(160deg, var(--brand), #2f8a6f 55%, #86c3a9);
      box-shadow:
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.4),
        0 10px 20px rgba(31,111,87,.22);
      position:relative;
      flex:0 0 auto;
    }

    .brand-mark::before,
    .brand-mark::after{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      background:#fff7e9;
      border-radius:99px;
    }

    .brand-mark::before{
      width:20px;
      height:4px;
      top:12px;
      left:12px;
      box-shadow:0 8px 0 #fff7e9, 0 16px 0 #fff7e9;
    }

    .brand-mark::after{
      width:6px;
      height:24px;
      right:10px;
      top:10px;
      opacity:.9;
    }

    .brand-copy{
      min-width:0;
    }

    .eyebrow{
      margin:0;
      font-size:.68rem;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.22em;
      color:var(--brand-3);
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .brand-title{
      margin:2px 0 0;
      font-family:"Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      font-size:1rem;
      line-height:1;
      font-weight:700;
      white-space:nowrap;
      overflow:hidden;
      text-overflow:ellipsis;
    }

    .menu-btn{
      border:none;
      background:var(--panel-solid);
      color:var(--text);
      width:46px;
      height:46px;
      border-radius:14px;
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      border:1px solid rgba(111,101,88,.12);
      cursor:pointer;
      transition:.25s ease;
    }

    .menu-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px) scale(1.02)}
    .menu-btn:active{transform:scale(.97)}

    .menu-icon{
      width:18px;
      height:14px;
      position:relative;
    }

    .menu-icon span{
      position:absolute;
      left:0;
      right:0;
      height:2px;
      border-radius:99px;
      background:var(--text);
      transition:.25s ease;
    }

    .menu-icon span:nth-child(1){top:0}
    .menu-icon span:nth-child(2){top:6px}
    .menu-icon span:nth-child(3){top:12px}

    body.menu-open .menu-icon span:nth-child(1){transform:translateY(6px) rotate(45deg)}
    body.menu-open .menu-icon span:nth-child(2){opacity:0}
    body.menu-open .menu-icon span:nth-child(3){transform:translateY(-6px) rotate(-45deg)}

    .drawer-backdrop{
      position:fixed;
      inset:0;
      background:rgba(24,20,15,.34);
      opacity:0;
      visibility:hidden;
      transition:.28s ease;
      z-index:40;
    }

    body.menu-open .drawer-backdrop{
      opacity:1;
      visibility:visible;
    }

    .drawer{
      position:fixed;
      top:0;
      right:0;
      width:min(86vw, 360px);
      height:100vh;
      z-index:50;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,250,240,.98), rgba(245,237,224,.98));
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      border-left:1px solid rgba(111,101,88,.14);
      box-shadow:-24px 0 60px rgba(30, 20, 8, .18);
      transform:translateX(100%);
      transition:transform .32s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1);
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      padding:18px;
    }

    body.menu-open .drawer{
      transform:translateX(0);
    }

    .drawer-top{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      margin-bottom:22px;
    }

    .close-btn{
      border:none;
      background:#f3eadb;
      width:42px;
      height:42px;
      border-radius:14px;
      font-size:1.2rem;
      cursor:pointer;
      color:var(--text);
    }

    .drawer-user{
      padding:16px;
      border:1px solid rgba(111,101,88,.12);
      border-radius:20px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.55);
      margin-bottom:18px;
    }

    .drawer-user strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:1rem;
      margin-bottom:4px;
    }

    .drawer-user span{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.92rem;
    }

    .drawer-nav{
      display:grid;
      gap:10px;
    }

    .drawer-nav a{
      text-decoration:none;
      color:var(--text);
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      padding:14px 14px;
      border-radius:16px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.5);
      border:1px solid rgba(111,101,88,.1);
      font-weight:700;
      transition:.22s ease;
    }

    .drawer-nav a:hover{
      transform:translateX(-4px);
      background:#fff;
    }

    .drawer-nav small{
      font-weight:600;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .drawer-logout{
      margin-top:auto;
      padding-top:18px;
    }

    .drawer-logout button{
      width:100%;
      border:none;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-3), #b54d36);
      color:white;
      padding:14px 18px;
      border-radius:16px;
      font-weight:800;
      font-family:inherit;
      cursor:pointer;
      box-shadow:0 16px 30px rgba(141,59,46,.22);
    }

    main{
      padding:14px 16px 100px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .hero{
      padding:18px 0 12px;
    }

    .hero h1{
      margin:8px 0 10px;
      font-family:"Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      font-size:clamp(2rem, 7vw, 3.3rem);
      line-height:.95;
      letter-spacing:-.04em;
      max-width:10ch;
    }

    .hero p{
      margin:0;
      color:var(--muted);
      line-height:1.6;
      max-width:34ch;
      font-size:.98rem;
    }

    .hero-chip{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:8px;
      padding:10px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:rgba(255,248,236,.8);
      border:1px solid rgba(111,101,88,.12);
      color:var(--brand-3);
      font-weight:800;
      font-size:.76rem;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.16em;
    }

    .hero-chip::before{
      content:"●";
      color:var(--brand);
      font-size:.8rem;
    }

    .summary{
      margin-top:18px;
      padding:18px;
      border-radius:28px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(31,111,87,.96), rgba(22,79,63,.96));
      color:#f8f4ec;
      box-shadow:0 24px 50px rgba(31,111,87,.24);
      overflow:hidden;
      position:relative;
    }

    .summary::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      width:160px;
      height:160px;
      right:-30px;
      top:-35px;
      border-radius:34px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,.14), rgba(255,255,255,0));
      transform:rotate(20deg);
    }

    .summary-top{
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      align-items:flex-start;
      gap:12px;
    }

    .summary h2{
      margin:0 0 8px;
      font-size:.8rem;
      letter-spacing:.2em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:#dceee7;
    }

    .summary p{
      margin:0;
      color:rgba(248,244,236,.8);
      line-height:1.5;
      max-width:26ch;
      font-size:.94rem;
    }

    .mini-badge{
      padding:10px 12px;
      border-radius:16px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
      font-size:.78rem;
      font-weight:700;
      white-space:nowrap;
    }

    .stats{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      gap:12px;
      margin-top:20px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .stat{
      padding:14px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
    }

    .stat span{
      display:block;
      font-size:.72rem;
      letter-spacing:.14em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:#d7ebe3;
      margin-bottom:8px;
      font-weight:700;
    }

    .stat strong{
      font-family:"Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      font-size:1.7rem;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
    }

    .section{
      margin-top:20px;
    }

    .section-head{
      display:flex;
      align-items:end;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:12px;
      margin-bottom:14px;
    }

    .section-head h3{
      margin:0;
      font-family:"Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      font-size:1.3rem;
      letter-spacing:-.03em;
    }

    .section-head p{
      margin:6px 0 0;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.92rem;
      line-height:1.5;
      max-width:28ch;
    }

    .quick-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap:12px;
    }

    .quick-link{
      text-decoration:none;
      color:var(--text);
      padding:16px 14px;
      border-radius:22px;
      background:rgba(255,250,240,.75);
      border:1px solid rgba(111,101,88,.12);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      min-height:118px;
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      justify-content:space-between;
      transition:.25s ease;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .quick-link:hover{
      transform:translateY(-4px);
      border-color:rgba(31,111,87,.25);
    }

    .quick-link::after{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      width:84px;
      height:84px;
      right:-18px;
      bottom:-18px;
      border-radius:24px;
      background:linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(31,111,87,.08), rgba(217,146,59,.08));
      transform:rotate(16deg);
    }

    .quick-icon{
      width:42px;
      height:42px;
      border-radius:14px;
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      font-size:1.1rem;
      background:#f1e6d2;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .quick-link:nth-child(1) .quick-icon{background:#efe0c6}
    .quick-link:nth-child(2) .quick-icon{background:#dceee7}
    .quick-link:nth-child(3) .quick-icon{background:#f3ddcf}
    .quick-link:nth-child(4) .quick-icon{background:#f1e1b4}
    .quick-link:nth-child(5){grid-column:1 / -1}

    .quick-copy{
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .quick-copy strong{
      display:block;
      font-size:1rem;
      margin-bottom:6px;
    }

    .quick-copy span{
      display:block;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.88rem;
      line-height:1.45;
      max-width:22ch;
    }

    .quick-arrow{
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
      font-weight:800;
      color:var(--brand);
      margin-top:10px;
    }

    .form-shell{
      padding:18px;
      border-radius:28px;
      background:rgba(255,250,240,.78);
      border:1px solid rgba(111,101,88,.12);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    form{
      display:grid;
      gap:14px;
    }

    .field{
      display:grid;
      gap:8px;
    }

    label{
      font-size:.86rem;
      font-weight:800;
      color:var(--brand-3);
      letter-spacing:.04em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
    }

    input, select, textarea{
      width:100%;
      border:none;
      outline:none;
      border-radius:16px;
      padding:15px 15px;
      font:inherit;
      color:var(--text);
      background:#fffdf8;
      border:1px solid rgba(111,101,88,.14);
      box-shadow:inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.55);
      transition:.2s ease;
    }

    input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus{
      border-color:rgba(31,111,87,.5);
      box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(31,111,87,.11);
      transform:translateY(-1px);
    }

    textarea{
      min-height:108px;
      resize:vertical;
    }

    .double{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      gap:12px;
    }

    .submit-btn{
      margin-top:4px;
      border:none;
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:16px 18px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-2), #e8b766 70%, #f4d18c);
      color:#2f200f;
      font-weight:800;
      font-size:1rem;
      font-family:inherit;
      cursor:pointer;
      box-shadow:0 18px 30px rgba(217,146,59,.23);
      transition:.25s ease;
    }

    .submit-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px) scale(1.01)}
    .submit-btn:active{transform:scale(.98)}

    .bottom-bar{
      position:fixed;
      left:50%;
      bottom:0;
      transform:translateX(-50%);
      width:min(100%, var(--max));
      z-index:25;
      padding:10px 14px calc(10px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(249,245,237,0), rgba(249,245,237,.95) 28%);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .bottom-inner{
      border-radius:24px;
      padding:10px 8px;
      background:rgba(255,250,240,.88);
      border:1px solid rgba(111,101,88,.12);
      box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(52,35,14,.14);
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap:6px;
    }

    .bottom-item{
      text-decoration:none;
      color:var(--muted);
      display:grid;
      justify-items:center;
      gap:6px;
      padding:8px 4px;
      border-radius:16px;
      font-size:.72rem;
      font-weight:800;
      transition:.2s ease;
    }

    .bottom-item .i{
      width:34px;
      height:34px;
      border-radius:12px;
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      background:transparent;
      color:var(--text);
      font-size:1rem;
      transition:.2s ease;
    }

    .bottom-item.active{
      color:var(--brand);
    }

    .bottom-item.active .i{
      background:#e1f0ea;
      color:var(--brand);
    }

    .bottom-item:hover .i{
      background:#f0e6d5;
    }

    .reveal{
      opacity:0;
      transform:translateY(18px);
      transition:opacity .7s ease, transform .7s ease;
    }

    .reveal.in-view{
      opacity:1;
      transform:translateY(0);
    }

    .stagger-1{transition-delay:.05s}
    .stagger-2{transition-delay:.12s}
    .stagger-3{transition-delay:.18s}
    .stagger-4{transition-delay:.24s}
    .stagger-5{transition-delay:.3s}

    @media (min-width: 700px){
      .app{
        max-width:920px;
      }

      main{
        padding:20px 22px 120px;
      }

      .hero h1{
        max-width:none;
      }

      .quick-grid{
        grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr);
      }

      .quick-link:nth-child(5){
        grid-column:auto;
      }

      .content-grid{
        display:grid;
        grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;
        gap:18px;
        align-items:start;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="drawer-backdrop" id="backdrop"></div>

  <aside class="drawer" id="drawer" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="drawer-top">
      <div class="brand-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Navigasi</p>
        <p class="brand-title">Menu Utama</p>
      </div>
      <button class="close-btn" id="closeMenu" aria-label="Tutup menu">✕</button>
    </div>

    <div class="drawer-user">
      <strong>Selamat Datang, admin</strong>
      <span>Kelola produk, penjualan, laporan, dan pengaturan dari satu tempat.</span>
    </div>

    <nav class="drawer-nav" aria-label="Navigasi utama">
      <a href="#dashboard"><span>⌂ Dashboard</span><small>Ringkasan</small></a>
      <a href="#produk"><span>▣ Produk</span><small>Stok</small></a>
      <a href="#penjualan"><span>↗ Penjualan</span><small>Transaksi</small></a>
      <a href="#laporan"><span>◫ Laporan</span><small>Analitik</small></a>
      <a href="#pengaturan"><span>⚙ Pengaturan</span><small>Preferensi</small></a>
    </nav>

    <div class="drawer-logout">
      <button type="button">Logout</button>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <div class="app texture">
    <header class="mobile-nav">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="brand-copy">
          <p class="eyebrow">KasirPro</p>
          <p class="brand-title">Admin Panel Mobile</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button class="menu-btn" id="menuToggle" aria-label="Buka menu" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="drawer">
        <div class="menu-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <span></span>
          <span></span>
          <span></span>
        </div>
      </button>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero reveal stagger-1" id="dashboard">
        <span class="hero-chip">Dashboard Admin</span>
        <h1>Versi mobile yang cepat, ringkas, dan nyaman.</h1>
        <p>Dirancang khusus untuk layar kecil agar input penjualan, akses menu utama, dan pemantauan toko tetap efisien saat bergerak.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="summary reveal stagger-2" aria-labelledby="ringkasan-title">
        <div class="summary-top">
          <div>
            <h2 id="ringkasan-title">Ringkasan Hari Ini</h2>
            <p>Kontrol penuh untuk operasional toko Anda dengan tampilan yang lebih fokus untuk penggunaan mobile.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mini-badge">Admin</div>
        </div>

        <div class="stats">
          <article class="stat">
            <span>Omzet Hari Ini</span>
            <strong>Rp 0</strong>
          </article>
          <article class="stat">
            <span>Cash di Laci</span>
            <strong>Rp 0</strong>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="content-grid">
        <section class="section reveal stagger-3" id="produk">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div>
              <h3>Akses Cepat</h3>
              <p>5 menu penting yang sering digunakan di dashboard admin.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="quick-grid">
            <a class="quick-link" href="#dashboard">
              <div class="quick-icon">⌂</div>
              <div class="quick-copy">
                <strong>Dashboard</strong>
                <span>Lihat ringkasan performa toko</span>
              </div>
              <div class="quick-arrow">→</div>
            </a>

            <a class="quick-link" href="#produk">
              <div class="quick-icon">▣</div>
              <div class="quick-copy">
                <strong>Produk</strong>
                <span>Kelola daftar dan stok produk</span>
              </div>
              <div class="quick-arrow">→</div>
            </a>

            <a class="quick-link" href="#penjualan">
              <div class="quick-icon">↗</div>
              <div class="quick-copy">
